CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 3, 1962, pg.14A, reads: "Pat Munioux, modeling Cox fashions, was one of the three interracial models in D.I. show"
TitMainTitle: Pat Munioux wearing dark sleeveless dress with tie at waist with fringe, dark gloves, and fur stole, standing on parquet floor in front of musicians in Holiday House for D.I. Club's "Melody in Fashion" benefit for MENDS
